short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Allows the saving and downloading of Kindroid.ai chats.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: KinLog allows the logging and downloading of Kindroid.ai chats for your permanent storage. KinLog will keep a historic log on your entire Kin or group chat and allow you to download it as text, HTML or JSON.
